This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of computational linguistics (cs.CL) as it deals with developing a question answering system for patient-specific questions over electronic health records. It also involves natural language processing techniques for annotating the dataset. Information retrieval (cs.IR) is another likely sub-category as the paper deals with retrieving relevant information from electronic health records. Machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) are also possible sub-categories as the paper mentions developing a question answering system powered by machine learning. Finally, database (cs.DB) is a possible sub-category as the paper deals with creating a dataset of questions and answers over patient records.
